==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Navajo'''

# (''native name:'' '''Diné bizaad''') an [[Apachean]] (Southern Athabaskan) language of the [[Athabascan]] language family belonging to the [[Na-Dené]] phylum. It is spoken by 149,000 people in the American Southwest (Arizona, New Mexico, Utah, and Colorado).

